  end

  subgraph G2["Group 2 - Canonical traffic admission and bus publication"]
    TRAFFIC["Canonical behavioural traffic<br>behavioural_streams only"]
    CONTRACT["Active ingress contract<br>execute-api base URL<br>stage v1<br>POST /ingest/push<br>X-IG-Api-Key"]
    HTTPAPI["Active external ingress boundary"]
    ALBSTALE["Retained internal ingress surface<br>stale boundary alternative"]
    DISPOSITION["Ingress disposition boundary<br>dedupe + admit / reject / quarantine / ambiguous truth"]
    IGDDB[("Ingress idempotency + admission truth")]
    TTRAFFIC[("Traffic topic")]
    TCTX[("Context topic family")]
    BUSHANDOFF["Closure point<br>authoritative runtime bus handoff"]
    RUNCTL["Ingest-commit closure"]
    EVID[("Run-scoped ingest evidence root")]
    INGEST["Closure point<br>committed ingest truth"]
  end

  CLAIM["Group claim<br>the platform turns canonical behavioural traffic into governed runtime entry truth"]

  TRAFFIC -->|must enter through| CONTRACT
  CONTRACT -->|lands at| HTTPAPI
  HTTPAPI -->|hands boundary-valid request into| DISPOSITION
  DISPOSITION -->|writes ingress truth into| IGDDB

  IGDDB -->|authoritative admitted traffic publishes to| TTRAFFIC
  IGDDB -->|authoritative admitted context publishes to| TCTX
  TTRAFFIC -->|together close| BUSHANDOFF
  TCTX -->|together close| BUSHANDOFF

  IGDDB -->|supplies admission basis to| RUNCTL
  BUSHANDOFF -->|supplies publish basis to| RUNCTL
  RUNCTL -->|commits receipt, quarantine, offset-proof, and verdict under| EVID
  EVID -->|closes as| INGEST

  ALBSTALE -. explicitly excluded from the accepted active-boundary story .-> HTTPAPI

  HTTPAPI -->|together prove| CLAIM
  DISPOSITION -->|together prove| CLAIM
  BUSHANDOFF -->|together prove| CLAIM
  INGEST -->|together prove| CLAIM
